AuthorName: AGHATHE N'GUESSAN
AuthorCountry: Cote D'Ivoire
Text: "I am on my first visit to Brazil for almost a quarter. I came here to spend\
  \ my annual leave and take training related to my professional life.\nIndeed, I\
  \ hold a Bachelor's degree and a Master's degree in Latin American literature, I\
  \ am enrolled in 3 years of doctorate of translation studies. Passionate about foreign\
  \ languages \u200B\u200Band communication, I speak fluently French, English, Spanish\
  \ and Portuguese. I work as a translator and interpreter.\nIn the hope that my application\
  \ will catch your attention, please receive my thanks in advance.\nThe applicant\n\
  Miss N'guessan Agathe"
